Package: rllmdoc
Title: Unified llms.txt Generation for Quarto and R Package Projects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates spec-compliant llms.txt and llms-full.txt files from
    Quarto website projects and R package (pkgdown) projects. Provides a
    unified interface that wraps native tooling, validates strictly against
    the llms.txt specification, and fails fast on missing metadata.
License: file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: quarto
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/artalytics/rllmdoc,
    https://docs.artalytics.dev/r/rllmdoc
BugReports: https://github.com/artalytics/rllmdoc/issues
